title: Four Eyes 1-4 (2008-2010) (Complete) (Minutemen)
description:
English | CBR | 4 Issues

Four Eyes #1-4
Publisher:  Image Comics
Publication Date:  October 1, 2008 - January 7, 2009

Writer:  Joe Kelly
Artist:  Max Fiumara
Colorist:  Nestor Pereyra
Letterer:  Drew Gill
Cover Artist:  Max Fiumara

Brooklyn 1930. America struggles in the grip of the Great Depression, and ten-year-old Enrico is willing to make any sacrifice to take care of his mother. Even if it means taking a job in the one place he's forbidden to go... the ring of fire where dragons are trained and fought for cash and glory.

Thanks goes to DTs, Zone, the Kid, Dizzy, and The Dame for this release.
